ROFILMING PHOTOGRAPHS.     SURVEYS BRIEFLY THE ALTERNATIVE METHODS OF MICROFILMING PHOTOGRAPHS WHICH AREAVAILABLE WITH CURRENT TECHNOLOGY; SUGGESTS QUESTIONS WHICH ARCHIVISTS ANDLIBRARIANS SHOULD ASK BEFORE COMMITING THEMSELVES TO PARTICULAR METHODS; ANDNOTES SOME HAZARDS INHERENT IN SPECIFIC METHODS. COLOUR MICROFORMS ARE NOTDISCUSSED, BUT SOURCES ON COLOUR MICROFORMING ARE MENTIONED